::::'''Young Master Gold:''' Tweet! You're an unfamiliar face. Is this your first time in Dreamville, tweet?
::::{{MC|f=The origami bird takes a fancy bow, then twirls its round body and touches the back of your hand gently.|m=The origami bird takes a fancy bow, then twirls its round body and assumes what seems to be a bow.}}
::::'''Young Master Gold:''' Welcome, {{MC|f=beautiful lady|m=handsome gentleman}}! Welcome to the town's grandest and most magnificent miracle &mdash; Goldleaf Plaza, tweet!
::;(If {{cx}}<!--performance 414034101 has not been seen-->)
::::'''Young Master Gold:''' Tweet? Oh my! If it isn't the kind traveler that I met before, tweet.
::::'''Young Master Gold:''' Hmm... You're just in time!
::::'''Young Master Gold:''' Welcome to the town's grandest and most magnificent miracle &mdash; Goldleaf Plaza, tweet!
:::{{DIcon|Arrow}} Goldleaf Plaza?
:::<!--Custom String Listener: TalkSentence_414030906-->
:::'''Young Master Gold:''' That's right, tweet! When we mention Dreamville's architecture, the most famous one will be the Goldleaf Plaza in front of you, {{MC|f=lady|m=gentleman}}, tweet.
:::'''Young Master Gold:''' Every branch has been placed meticulously, and it's embellished with gold leaves and sparkling jewels, tweet! Combining both aesthetics and utility is none other than Dreamville's Goldleaf Plaza, tweet!
:::{{DIcon|Arrow}} That's so cool!
::::<!--Custom String Listener: TalkSentence_414030909-->
::::'''Young Master Gold:''' Tweet tweet! {{MC|f=Lady|m=Gentleman}}, you do have a good eye, tweet!
:::{{DIcon|Arrow}} Underwhelming.
::::<!--Custom String Listener: TalkSentence_414030911-->
::::'''Young Master Gold:''' Uh-huh, that's fine, tweet! Time will filter out better works out for us, tweet!
:::{{DIcon|Arrow}} I've met someone like you...
::::<!--Custom String Listener: TalkSentence_414030913-->
::::The bright golden hue, that flamboyant tone, the way you flaunt your wealth... You've definitely seen these traits in *someone*.
::::'''Young Master Gold:''' Oho? Dreamville has guests like that, tweet?
::::{{DIcon|Arrow}} It's a golden guy.
:::::<!--Custom String Listener: TalkSentence_414030916-->
:::::'''Young Master Gold:''' Tweet tweet! Must be a sophisticated artist!
::::{{DIcon|Arrow}} It's an ostentatious one.
:::::<!--Custom String Listener: TalkSentence_414030918-->
:::::'''Young Master Gold:''' Ahem, ahem, I've already toned it down plenty, tweet...
::::{{DIcon|Arrow}} It's a dangerous one.
:::::<!--Custom String Listener: TalkSentence_414030920-->
:::::'''Young Master Gold:''' Hehe, danger can be attractive too, tweet!
:::::Of course, the danger you speak of doesn't mean this at all.
:::<!--Custom String Trigger: TalkSentence_414030922-->
:::<!--Custom String Listener: TalkSentence_414030922-->
:::'''Young Master Gold:''' A pity, since the actual Goldleaf Plaza should be grander and shinier, tweet!
:::'''Young Master Gold:''' Everyone loves the Goldleaf Plaza, but there's always an idiot who doesn't appreciate its beauty, and even wants to usurp my creation, tweet!
:::'''Young Master Gold:''' Many of the gems in the plaza have also been stolen, and my assistants have been scared off by Boss Stone, tweet...
:::'''Young Master Gold:''' Please help me find those missing birds, tweet!
:::{{DIcon|Arrow}} I'll help you find them.
::::<!--Custom String Listener: TalkSentence_414030927-->
::::'''Young Master Gold:''' Mhmm, quick decision. I wasn't wrong about you being a good helper tweet!
:::{{DIcon|Arrow}} I'll help you find the gems.
::::<!--Custom String Listener: TalkSentence_414030929-->
::::'''Young Master Gold:''' I'm never out of gems, but little old me can't possibly complete the Goldleaf Plaza alone, tweet!
:::{{DIcon|Arrow}} I'll help you beat people up.
::::<!--Custom String Listener: TalkSentence_414030931-->
::::'''Young Master Gold:''' Tweet tweet tweet! Gentle birds battle with their tongues, never their talons, tweet!
:::<!--Custom String Trigger: TalkSentence_414030932-->
